query:
/*+  */ select t1.name,
count(*)
from question AS q1
inner join tag_question AS tq1
on q1.id = tq1.question_id AND q1.view_count >= 10 AND q1.view_count <= 1000
inner join tag AS t1
on t1.id = tq1.tag_id AND t1.name IN ('angular',
'asp.net',
'c++',
'delphi',
'laravel',
'node.js',
'orientação-a-objetos',
'postgresql',
'python-3.x',
'query',
'regex',
'string',
'winforms',
'wordpress',
'xml')
inner join answer AS a1
on a1.question_id = q1.id
inner join site AS s
on s.site_id = t1.site_id AND s.site_id = a1.site_id AND s.site_id = q1.site_id AND s.site_id = tq1.site_id AND s.site_name IN ('pt')
inner join so_user AS u1
on s.site_id = u1.site_id AND a1.owner_user_id = u1.id AND q1.owner_user_id = u1.id AND u1.upvotes >= 0 AND u1.upvotes <= 1 group by t1.name;
